Which version of pyang do you use? I can't reproduce the problem, it seems to work OK:
```
$ cat test.yang
module test {
  namespace "http://example.com/test";
  prefix t;

  container configs {
    container profiles {
      list profile {
        key "name";
        leaf name {
          type string;
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
$ cat test-data.xml 
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<data xmlns="urn:ietf:params:xml:ns:netconf:base:1.0">
  <configs xmlns="http://example.com/test">
    <profiles>
      <profile>
	<name>default-profile</name>
      </profile>
    </profiles>
